{"tid":2037441,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"太古廣場黑狗：連登仔又後送頭","createTime":"2020-05-27T03:41:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T05:06:54.000Z","uid":4959,"like":16,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"42bb8c81b57d925a59fb5890ed5d218a9d5451ec","tid":2037441,"uid":4959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:41:35.000Z","msg":"三青年太古廣場外被截查<br />\n警：連登仔嚟送頭？<br />\n<br />\n【即時】(10:28) 立法會今日恢復二讀《國歌法》，有網民號召「大三罷」及包圍立法會，警方今早加強在金鐘一帶戒備，多名市民被截查，部分更被帶走。<br />\n<br />\n太古廣場外有三名青年被十多名警員截查逾30分鐘。蕭先生表示他們是朋友，今早走到太古廣場外突然被警員包圍，並要求搜查背囊。黎先生指，在截查期間遭到警員以粗口指罵，斥「信唔信我拉鳩你？」他又指身旁一個較高級的警員對他嚷「做乜撚嘢？我而家唔撚妥你呀！」，更斥「連登仔嚟送頭？」<br />\n<br />\n他們三人被放行後，表示不會因而離開金鐘一帶，會因應情況，先在附近閒逛。"},{"pid":"0329deabb40221e6920e9c4e3670f6cb978922b1","tid":2037441,"uid":254745,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:45:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">返shift狗去猝死？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"2afe77c41a221e528a9745a44b6e059c436f4f31","tid":2037441,"uid":254745,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:46:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">返shift賤種黑狗去猝死？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2a0d3fe3075b492e478894ad751c260d751dd4f2","tid":2037441,"uid":254745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:49:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af5afad374f464789b6ed86e9c244d6def9f1157","tid":2037441,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:50:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/as